Package edu.uchsc.ccp.dmap

Interface Summary
DMAPPropertyFunctionHandler This interface allows external objects to handle DMAP slot property functions.
IReferenceHandler This is the interface that a Java class needs to implement in order to be a valid Reference handler withing OpenDMAP.
 

Class Summary
ASTConverter Processor for DMAP recognition patterns.
DefaultTokenizer The DefaultTokenizer is used to create a token sequence when an input string is handed to the Parser.
DMAPItem A DMAPItem is the basic unit of recognition in OpenDMAP.
DMAPLogger A facility for logging tracing messages in various ways.
DMAPToken A DMAPToken is an input concept for the Parser.
DMAPTokenizer This class is the root of all DMAPTokenizer objects.
FramePredictionMap Implements a mapping from Protege frame pattern items to predictions.
HandlerTable This class implements a table of reference handlers for the OpenDMAP parser.
InfoPacket An InfoPacket is a binding between a DMAPItem that was expected in a pattern, and the specific value, or Reference that was matched against that item.
LogFormatter  
Parser The parser is the main entry point into the OpenDMAP system.
Pattern A pattern is what DMAP is looking to find in the input text.
PatternGroup A PatternGroup is a collection of pattern fragments that are all waiting for the same next parser item to be recognized.
Prediction A Prediction is the heart of the DMAP parsing process.
PredictionEnvironment This class defines a binding environment for the pattern property constraints used by a prediction.
PredictionManager This class manages the set of predictions needed by the parser.
PredictionTable This class holds a set of DMAP predictions.
ProtegeFrameItem This class represents a Protege Frame in DMAP.
ProtegeProjectGroup This class represents a collection of Protege Knowledge Bases that are being used together in the OpenDMAP parser.
ProtegeSlotItem This class represents a Protege Slot.
Reference A Reference is a description of something that DMAP has recognized in the input text.
RegexItem This class represents a regular expression to be matched against input text strings.
StringPredictionMap Implements a mapping from string-based pattern items to predictions.
TextItem This class represents a text string within DMAP.
 

Enum Summary
Pattern.Operator  
 

Exception Summary
DMAPPropertyFunctionException An exception to be thrown when an external object has a problem evaluating a property function.
